---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Longer bio and background."
  currentPath="/about"
>
  <section class="content-body">
    <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
    <h1>Longer Bio</h1>
    <p>
      I am an engineer who likes systems that stay legible under pressure. Most of my
      work sits somewhere between product engineering, infrastructure, and practical
      tooling.
    </p>
    <p>
      I care about maintainability, explicit tradeoffs, and interfaces that do not hide
      how they work. That usually means static sites over dashboards, plain text over
      control panels, and simple deployment paths over impressive architecture diagrams.
    </p>
    <p>
      Outside of client and product work, I keep a running archive of notes, small
      experiments, and references that earn their place by being useful more than once.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
